|               |  Limit: skip=0, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |   Sort: u DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |     Projection: hits.RegionID, count(DISTINCT hits.UserID) AS u                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
